<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11563</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14307</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹迷路了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14308</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17432</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>似乎没有人听到他的呼救声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17433</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22979</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在他快要失去希望的时候，他听到了脚步声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22980</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28797</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“下午好，匹诺曹。”一只狐狸走了过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28798</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31361</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狐狸拄着拐杖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31362</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36475</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的身边站着一只用绷带缠着眼睛的猫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36476</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39574</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是谁？”匹诺曹说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39575</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你怎么知道我的名字？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44970</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50171</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们看到你的父亲杰佩托在村子里面到处找你。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50172</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他请求全体村民帮助他，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52604</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是没有人知道在哪里可以找到你。”猫说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62973</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可怜的爸爸。他在这么寒冷的天气里找我。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62974</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他一定很担心。我必须赶快回家，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68117</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73796</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>告诉他现在我们是有钱人了。”匹诺曹说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73797</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81659</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一听这话，猫从绷带下偷偷地看了一眼，狐狸挺起背站得笔直。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81660</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84790</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，匹诺曹没有注意到。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84791</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88886</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> “什么？有钱？”狐狸问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88887</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93893</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一个小木头人怎么会有钱呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93894</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99815</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我……呃……我赚来的。”匹诺曹撒了谎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99816</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104544</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“赚的吗？怎么赚的钱？”猫问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104545</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108937</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我曾经为一位木偶师傅跳舞，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108938</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114063</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>是他付给我的钱。”匹诺曹再次撒谎道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114064</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119782</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不相信像你这样的一个小男孩儿可以有很多钱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119783</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124396</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你必须给我看看我才能相信你。”猫说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124397</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128422</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，你看不到它。”匹诺曹说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128423</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132182</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我已经把它们藏起来了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132183</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138440</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他并没有觉得一只瞎眼的猫要求看他的金子是一件多么奇怪的事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138441</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144962</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你只能带这么点钱给你爸爸，真是可惜。”狐狸说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144963</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147765</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他是多么善良的一个人啊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147766</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153151</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我知道有一个办法可以把很少的钱变成很多的钱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157589</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是我想你肯定不会感兴趣的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157590</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>来吧，猫先生，我们告诉匹诺曹回家的路就好了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163137</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是说我可以有更多的钱吗？”匹诺曹问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169936</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172766</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他对这件事感到很惊讶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172767</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175291</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我需要工作吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175292</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178794</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，不用！”猫笑着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178795</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182279</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们绝不会建议你做这样的傻事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182280</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187449</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们知道一块秘密的土地，叫做傻瓜福地。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187450</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192460</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果你把你的钱在半夜里种下去，给它浇上水，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192461</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198447</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天再回来的时候，它就会长成一棵摇钱树。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198448</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205314</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇，那我们就真的变成有钱人了！”匹诺曹说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205315</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210976</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他想起蟋蟀先生说过，诚实的工作是赚钱的最佳途径。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210977</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，如果我有很多钱，杰佩托会更加爱我的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223822</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>请你快告诉我这块儿地在哪里吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223823</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228710</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是，他们出发去寻找那块神奇的土地了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228711</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233709</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们走了一整天，一直走到晚上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233710</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239223</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“欢迎来到傻瓜福地，匹诺曹。”猫说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239224</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244166</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你可以把金子种在你想要摇钱树生长的位置。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244167</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246989</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹非常兴奋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246990</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254388</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他挖了一个洞，小心地把黄金放到里面，然后盖上了泥土。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254389</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259597</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，你应该浇水。在你去找水的时候，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259598</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264520</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猫先生和我会在这里帮你守护你的钱。”狐狸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264521</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>匹诺曹并没有觉得一只瞎眼的猫来帮他看钱是一件多么奇怪的事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275508</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他跑开了，然后迅速地拎回了一桶水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275509</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280976</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>给金子浇完水之后，剩下的就只是等待了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280977</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284499</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，我们去附近找一个谷仓吧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284500</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288647</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那样我们就可以休息一会儿了。”猫说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288648</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293507</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，如果我们留在这儿看着，树就不会长成。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293508</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295339</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狐狸赞同地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295340</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303248</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是，带着马上就会发财的想法，他们离开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>